dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains information about wind turbines in the United States, including location, dates of operation, status, proximity to nearest airport, and representative contact information. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2013 Spring Quarter update (Update 1011).This layer can be used to locate wind tubines in the United States.
